---
// Widget / Dynamic Island ショーケース（CSS モック、実装準拠）
---

<section class="showcase">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="eyebrow">ホーム画面から、ロック画面から</span>
      <h2>アプリを開かなくても、学習は続く</h2>
      <p>
        ウィジェット・Dynamic Island・ロック画面に今日の単語が現れる。<br />
        思い出した瞬間、その場で回答して SRS が更新されます。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stage">
      <!-- ===== Dynamic Island（展開表示・裏面） ===== -->
      <figure class="card reveal">
        <div class="label">Dynamic Island</div>
        <div class="phone" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="screen di-screen">
            <span class="sb-time">9:41</span>
            <span class="sb-battery"></span>
            <div class="island">
              <div class="island-row">
                <span class="emoji">📚</span>
                <span class="counter dark">2 / 5</span>
              </div>
              <div class="word">
                <span class="front dark">acquire</span>
                <span class="back white">→  獲得する</span>
              </div>
              <div class="answers">
                <span class="pill red">✗ 知らなかった</span>
                <span class="pill green">✓ 知ってた</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figcaption>他アプリ中でも展開して回答 → 即 SRS 更新。</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <!-- ===== ホーム画面ウィジェット（裏面） ===== -->
      <figure class="card reveal">
        <div class="label">ホーム画面ウィジェット</div>
        <div class="phone" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="screen hs-screen">
            <span class="sb-time dark-bg">9:41</span>
            <span class="sb-battery dark-bg"></span>
            <div class="widget">
              <div class="w-head">
                <span class="sess">📚 今日の復習</span>
                <span class="counter muted">2 / 5</span>
              </div>
              <div class="word">
                <span class="front muted">acquire</span>
                <span class="back">→  獲得する</span>
              </div>
              <div class="answers">
                <span class="pill red">✗ 知らなかった</span>
                <span class="pill green">✓ 知ってた</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dock-hint">
              <span class="dock-icon"></span>
              <span class="dock-icon"></span>
              <span class="dock-icon"></span>
              <span class="dock-icon"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figcaption>タップ一つで回答、そのまま習熟度に反映。</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .showcase {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 0%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 10%, transparent), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 90% 100%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.08), transparent 50%);
  }
  .inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .heading { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 10%, transparent);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .heading p {
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .stage {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .card { margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  figcaption {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  /* ---- Phone frame (shared) ---- */
  .phone {
    width: 320px;
    height: 420px;
    border-radius: 52px;
    padding: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1f2937, #0f172a);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.35);
  }
  .screen {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 44px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .sb-time, .sb-battery {
    position: absolute;
    top: 14px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .sb-time { left: 22px; }
  .sb-battery {
    right: 22px;
    top: 18px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 70%);
  }
  .sb-time.dark-bg { color: #fff; mix-blend-mode: difference; }
  .sb-battery.dark-bg { mix-blend-mode: difference; }

  /* ---- Dynamic Island screen (dark wallpaper) ---- */
  .di-screen {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 80%, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.25), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0b0b18, #1a1033 80%);
  }
  .island {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: #000;
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 10px 14px 12px;
    width: 240px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04),
      0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    animation: islandBreathe 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes islandBreathe {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-1px); }
  }
  .island-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .emoji { font-size: 14px; }
  .counter {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .counter.dark { color: #9ca3af; }
  .counter.muted { color: #6b7280; }

  /* ---- Shared word line ---- */
  .word {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: 4px 0 6px;
  }
  .front {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .front.dark { color: #9ca3af; }
  .front.muted { color: #6b7280; }
  .back {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #111;
  }
  .back.white { color: #fff; }

  /* ---- Answer pills ---- */
  .answers {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .pill.red { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.18); color: #ef4444; }
  .pill.green { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18); color: #16a34a; }

  /* ---- Home screen ---- */
  .hs-screen {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(160deg, #7c3aed, #4f46e5 55%, #0891b2);
  }
  .widget {
    position: absolute;
    top: 90px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 220px;
    height: 160px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    border-radius: 22px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    animation: widgetFloat 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes widgetFloat {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-3px); }
  }
  .w-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 10.5px;
  }
  .sess { color: #6b7280; font-weight: 500; }
  .dock-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .dock-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .island, .widget { animation: none; }
    .island { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    .widget { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stage {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
